	<summary>Manage Blood Pressure Data</summary>
	<description>
		<p>
			Manage your blood pressure data with UBPM.
			Display data as chart, table or statistics and print for the doctor.
			Analyze data via SQL queries.
			The measurements can be entered manually, imported from file or read directly from supported blood pressure monitors and exported to CSV, XML, JSON or SQLite.
		</p>
